---
import ServiceLayout from "../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro";
const phoneNumber = import.meta.env.PHONE_NUMBER;
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="24 Hour Mobile Tyre Fitting | Tyre Emergency Ltd"
  description="Flat tyre? Tyre Emergency provides quick, reliable, 24-hour mobile tyre fitting in Nottinghamshire. Call now and get back on the road fast."
  heading="Stuck With a Flat Tyre?"
  tagline="We come to you — fast. Call now and we’ll be there in 30 minutes or less."
  backgroundUrl="/img/tyre.jpeg"
>
  <h1 class="mb-3">
    Tyre Emergency - Your Local Mobile Tyre Fitting Specialists
  </h1>
  <p>
    <em
      ><span class="fw-bold">If you’ve got a flat tyre, we can help.</span> Tyre
      Emergency comes straight to you, wherever you are, to get your tyre sorted
      quickly—often in less than an hour.</em>
  </p>
  <p>
    We provide 24-hour mobile tyre fitting across Nottinghamshire. Whether
    you’re at home, at work, or stuck by the roadside, we’ll handle everything
    from puncture repairs to replacing your tyre. Our goal is to get you moving
    again safely and without hassle.
  </p>

  <h2 class="">We Cover Nottinghamshire</h2>
  <p>
    We serve Nottinghamshire and nearby areas, including Nottingham, Mansfield,
    Worksop, and Newark-on-Trent. Not sure if we can reach you? Just give us a
    call to find out.
  </p>

  <h2 class="">Why Choose Us</h2>
  <p>
    We understand how frustrating a flat tyre can be, which is why we aim to
    reach you quickly—usually in under an hour, no matter the time of day. With
    over ten years of experience, we’re confident in our ability to fix the
    problem and get you back on the road. Plus, our pricing is always clear,
    with no hidden surprises.
  </p>

  <h2 class="">Call Us Today</h2>
  <p>
    Getting help is easy. Call us now at <a
      href=`tel:${phoneNumber}`
      class="link-danger">{phoneNumber}</a
    >, let us know your tyre details and location, and we’ll provide a quote and
    let you know how soon we’ll arrive. Don’t let a flat tyre ruin your
    plans—Tyre Emergency is here to help, 24/7.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
